    <text xml:lang="en">
        <body>
            <head>
                <title>A Winter's Ball</title>
            </head>
            <div type="song">

                <sp who="#burr">
                    <speaker>BURR</speaker>
                    <l>How does the bastard, orphan, son of a whore</l>
                    <l>Go on and on</l>
                    <l>Grow into more of a phenomenon?</l>
                    <l>Watch this obnoxious, arrogant, loudmouth bother</l>
                    <l>Be seated at the right hand of the father</l>
                    <l><persName ref="#washington">Washington</persName> hires <persName ref="#hamilton">Hamilton</persName> right on sight</l>
                    <l>But <persName ref="#hamilton">Hamilton</persName> still wants to fight, not
                        write</l>
                    <l>Now <persName ref="#hamilton">Hamilton’s</persName> skill with a quill is
                        undeniable</l>
                    <l>But what do we have in common? We’re</l>
                    <l>Reliable with the</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#men">
                    <speaker>MEN</speaker>
                    <l>Ladies!</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#burr">
                    <speaker>BURR</speaker>
                    <l>There are so many to deflower!</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#men">
                    <speaker>MEN</speaker>
                    <l>Ladies!</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#burr">
                    <speaker>BURR</speaker>
                    <l>Looks! Proximity to power</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#men">
                    <speaker>MEN</speaker>
                    <l>Ladies!</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#burr">
                    <speaker>BURR</speaker>
                    <l>They delighted and distracted him</l>
                    <l><persName ref="#marthaWashington">Martha Washington</persName> named her
                        feral tomcat after him!</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#hamilton">
                    <speaker>HAMILTON</speaker>
                    <l>That’s true!</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#company">
                    <speaker>COMPANY</speaker>
                    <l><date>1780</date></l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#burr">
                    <speaker>BURR</speaker>
                    <l>A winter’s ball</l>
                    <l>And the <persName ref="#schuylerSis">Schuyler sisters</persName> are the envy
                        of all</l>
                    <l>Yo, if you can marry a sister, you’re rich, son</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#hamilton">
                    <speaker>HAMILTON</speaker>
                    <l>Is it a question of if, <persName ref="#burr">Burr</persName>, or which
                        one?</l>
                </sp>

                <sp who="#hamilton #burr #laurens">
                    <speaker>HAMILTON/BURR/LAURENS</speaker>
                    <l>Hey</l>
                    <l>Hey</l>
                    <l>Hey hey</l>
                </sp>
            </div>
